### Svae

For the SVAE[20], the latent state prior is a linear dynamical system parameterized as,

\[p_{\theta}(\mathbf{z}_{t}\,|\,\mathbf{z}_{t-1})=\mathcal{N}(\mathbf{z}_{t}\,|\, \mathbf{F}\mathbf{z}_{t-1},\mathbf{Q})\] (90)

